name: 2 Astronauts: Co-Dependency
description:
2 Astronauts: Co-Dependency

I've been reflecting on how much we need each other in Web3.
Where are we going?
Who got there/here first?
How are we traveling?
Who it taking?
Who is offering?
Are we working for/with or against each other?
How will be get home, or not, together?
#neverleavequietly
